"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1928932-2024-Paris-Olympics-triathlon-postponed\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  There has been more chaos at the2024 Paris Oympicsafter triathlon competitors had a training session postponed.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 113, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The River Seine was due to be the scene of a practice swimming session today (Sunday), but that has been scuppered due to water condtions.\", \"from\": 114, \"to\": 252, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 118, \"end\": 129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers have released a statement confirming the decision, which followed examinations on Saturday.\", \"from\": 254, \"to\": 356, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Paris 2024 and World Triathlon reiterate that the priority is the health of the athletes,\\\" they said.\", \"from\": 358, \"to\": 460, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 374, \"end\": 389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\", \"score\": 0.9999999846922948, \"rank\": 1.5307497399413528e-08, \"text\": \"World Triathlon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The analysis carried out yesterday in the Seine showed water quality levels that do not present sufficient guarantees to allow the event to take place.\", \"from\": 461, \"to\": 613, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 504, \"end\": 509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 1.7582946052434783e-12, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pick up your ultimate guide to the Olympics!\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 659, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Going for Gold provides the day-by-day rundown of what's on and when.\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 729, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clickhereto buy.\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 746, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The competition is still set to start as planned on Tuesday, with the statement adding: \\\"Given the weather forecast for the next 48 hours, Paris 2024 and World Triathlon are confident that water quality will return to below limits before the start for of the triathlon competitions.\\\"\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 1031, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 887, \"end\": 897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.6674735072180254e-26, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 902, \"end\": 917, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\", \"score\": 0.9999999846922948, \"rank\": 1.5307497399413528e-08, \"text\": \"World Triathlon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Contingency plans are reportedly in place if conditions in the river do not sufficiently improve.\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1130, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Vaires-sur-Marne, on the Marne river east of Paris, is a back-up option for both the triathlon and swimming marathon.\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1248, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1176, \"end\": 1181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.32257264841701e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The swimming leg of the familiarisation had been due to take place at 7am this morning.\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1337, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The bike and running training however, will go ahead as scheduled.\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1448, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1519, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1513, \"end\": 1518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.32257264841701e-17, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1624, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1594, \"end\": 1606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9986201193236169, \"rank\": 0.001381781875816241, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1679, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The development means further schedule disruption after inclement weather plagued the opening day on Saturday.\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1793, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A skateboarding event was postponed while thetennisat Roland Garros was hit by delays.\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1880, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1848, \"end\": 1861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"score\": 0.9928563640054441, \"rank\": 0.0071950346604661595, \"text\": \"Roland Garros\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Friday's opening ceremony was also plagued by heavy rain, with many participants using umbrellas to shield themselves.\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 2000, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The water in the river had already been the subject of concern in the build-up to the summer Games, with tests as recently as June showing traces of E.coli.\", \"from\": 2001, \"to\": 2157, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Last week, Paris Mayor Anne Hidalgo and Paris 2024 chief Tony Estanguet publicly swam in the Seine in a bid to allay fears.\", \"from\": 2159, \"to\": 2282, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2170, \"end\": 2181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Mayor\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2182, \"end\": 2194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anne Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\"}, {\"begin\": 2199, \"end\": 2209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.6674735072180254e-26, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2216, \"end\": 2230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}, {\"begin\": 2252, \"end\": 2257, \"title\": \